A = C C^T
A>0
A=\begin{bmatrix} a & b \\ b & c\end{bmatrix} 
C =\begin{bmatrix} \alpha & 0 \\ \beta & \gamma\end{bmatrix} 
\alpha = \sqrt{a}
\beta = { b \over \sqrt{a} }
\gamma = \sqrt{c-{b^2 \over a}}
C = \begin{bmatrix} 2 & 0 \\ { 1 \over 2} & {\sqrt{7} \over 2} \end{bmatrix} 
